147688.<color_yellow>\nデッキの編成の 説明です！\n<br>\nモンス:
This will explain Deck Editing!
By putting 20 Monster Tarots into a deck and equipping it, you can use those cards during battle.
If an equipped deck has less than 20 Monster Tarots in it, it cannot be used in battle.
There is a limit to the amount of each Tarot that can be included in a deck, and you cannot build one with all the same cards.
If you've included too many of a particular Tarot, you will see a "!" mark appear. You cannot use a deck with this mark.
